export default () => `
Hi thanks for visiting,this site is here to educate you on choosing the proper stick for you.

Click on tabs above(USA/Japan/???)to find out more. Below I have reason why you should choose arcades sticks verus using a regular gaming pad.

When using arcade sticks they are most used on fighters,shooters,and all old school games you played when you were a kid such as frogger or pacman.

Larger Buttons

  • easier to press and do combos
  • cooler looking
  • clicky noises

Joysticks

  • Joysticks=better movement
  • Faster inputs
  • clicky noises

`;
